			"id": "47029495-8cb3195f-9697-4dd2-b371-7fa0eab5752f",
			"description": "Structured output endpoint — returns a ResearchBrief JSON object instead of free text.\n\nMERN analogy: like Vercel AI SDK generateObject() + Zod schema.\nSpring AI calls .entity(ResearchBrief.class) which auto-generates a JSON schema,\nappends it to the prompt, and deserialises the model's JSON response.\n\nRequest:  { \"topic\": string }   — @NotBlank validated\nResponse: ResearchBrief { topic, keyFindings[], risks[], nextQuestions[] }\n\nBook ref: Chapter 5 — Structured Output."
